1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
After the fox demon left, Shen Nian didn't rush to the Emperor.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
She went back to the dry well first.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,000
You... came back again.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,000
I need to refine something here.

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,000
A hundred-year snake demon — mediocre quality.

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:19,000
But for you right now — it's enough.

7
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:23,000
The moment the cold liquid touched her palm —

8
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:27,000
[Refinable demon blood detected. Refine? Yes / No]

9
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Yes.

10
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,000
An icy force surged from her palm.

11
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:37,000
Demon Bloodline boiling — dark-gold patterns emerged.

12
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:40,000
The Demon Emperor bloodline is indeed dominant.

13
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Ice complements you — your Frost Mastery will rise a tier.

14
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
The snake's qi was cold and savage — a viper raging within.

15
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
The Demon Bloodline a tiger — devouring every drop.

16
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:56,000
The Seal Maiden rose — pressed a small hand to her brow.

17
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:59,000
A golden rune — flowed into Shen Nian's brow.

18
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Thank you.

19
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Don't talk — focus.

20
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:07,000
[Refining complete. Ice shards 1→20, Ice wall 5 inches]

21
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:11,000
[New skill "Ice Seal" — freeze 3 zhang ground for 5 breaths]

22
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Ice shard pierced stone 3 inches deep — frost spread around.

23
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,000
More than double the power.

24
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:21,000
Silver-rank demon mid-tier — barely safe in the palace.

25
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:24,000
But against a real Demon King — you can't even flee.

26
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:27,000
I know. That's why I'm going — to the frontier.

27
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:31,000
A thousand-year Tiger Demon — to ascend to Gold-rank.

28
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:35,000
Thousand-year Tiger Demon — Gold-rank mid-tier.

29
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:38,000
You're only Silver-rank early — two tiers short.

30
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:41,000
If you go — you'll die.

31
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:44,000
Who says I'll fight head-on? I'm human — not demon.

32
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:48,000
Humans can borrow blades, set traps, use poison.

33
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:52,000
The Seal paused — then her lips slightly upturned.

34
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:55,000
Interesting. Of every Demon Emperor heir I've seen —

35
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,000
you are the most cunning.

36
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:59,000
That's called — wisdom.

37
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:02,000
What do you want then? A book?

38
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Bring a person.

39
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,000
Who?

40
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:09,000
The Seal didn't answer — became a statue again.

41
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:13,000
Back above ground — dawn was breaking.

42
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:16,000
The eastern sky paled — the palace took shape.

43
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:19,000
Shen Nian stood by the well — and drew a deep breath.

44
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,000
A new day — a new beginning.
